name: Jaywalkers
description:
Inside this low-poly universe is a low-poly city with low poly laws. As a member of a gang of law breakers, your goal is to make your way up through the ranks and prove yourself by committing the ultimate crime. Jaywalking. With only one goal in mind, you do whatever it takes to surpass the top dog and take the title and glory as 'The Ultimate Jaywalker.' 

Think you got what it takes to get on the leaderboard?
